episodes.title: Pilot
episodes.plot: A mobster passes out at a family barbecue and seeks therapy to understand why.

episodes.title: 46 Long
episodes.plot: Tony is getting fed up with his mother. Brendan Filone acts against Tony's wishes. Salvatore and Paulie try to track down A.J.'s teacher's stolen car.

episodes.title: Denial, Anger, Acceptance
episodes.plot: Tony encourages an unwanted son-in-law to divorce, Carmela learns another secret of Tony's, Meadow experiments with speed to study for the SATs, and Chris and Brendan find out the price of disrespecting Junior.

episodes.title: Meadowlands
episodes.plot: Brendan's death leaves Chris fearing for his life, and Anthony's discovery of what his father really does leaves him confused.

episodes.title: College
episodes.plot: While visiting colleges with Meadow, Tony spots a snitch. Carmela, meanwhile, discovers something about Dr. Melfi.

episodes.title: Pax Soprana
episodes.plot: Tony tries to balance Junior against the other capos, while Carmela reasserts herself as the woman in Tony's life.

episodes.title: Down Neck
episodes.plot: Anthony has disciplinary problems at school, prompting Tony to recount memories of his childhood with Dr. Melfi.

episodes.title: The Legend of Tennessee Moltisanti
episodes.plot: The FBI begins closing in on the DiMeo family. Tony and Carmela are angry over all the attention Italians get from the authorities, while Chris fumes that he's not getting enough attention.

episodes.title: Boca
episodes.plot: The capos discuss what to do about the local soccer coach, while Junior's mouth causes him some embarrassment.

episodes.title: A Hit Is a Hit
episodes.plot: Tony tries to branch out into legitimate investments, while Chris and Adriana decide to try their hands at music production.

episodes.title: Nobody Knows Anything
episodes.plot: Following the arrest of two of his men, Tony suspects a traitor. Efforts to discover who, however, are stymied.

episodes.title: Isabella
episodes.plot: The stress Tony is going through begins to take its toll, and the hit Junior has ordered doesn't help.

episodes.title: I Dream of Jeannie Cusamano
episodes.plot: Tony starts cleaning house, while Artie feels torn between keeping the peace in his household, and getting even with Tony for destroying his restaurant.
